      "body" : "I don't think you have a weird configuration, and don't see any harm in supporting it. However, I don't think this is the right solution to your problem.\r\n\r\nLooking at the root of the issue: why is `fs::create_directory` called when the symlink already exists?\r\n",
      "created_at" : "2013-05-05T13:52:52Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/2590#issuecomment-17452038",
      "id" : 17452038,
      "issue_url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/2590",
      "updated_at" : "2013-05-05T13:52:52Z",
      "url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/comments/17452038",
      "user" : {
         "avatar_url" : "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/126646?v=3",
         "events_url" : "https://api.github.com/users/laanwj/events{/privacy}",
         "followers_url" : "https://api.github.com/users/laanwj/followers",
